{"tid":876903,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【窩心男孩】女童搭巴士首來潮 男童遞衞衣：我姊妹都係咁無事嘅","createTime":"2018-10-26T03:12:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-26T04:31:44.000Z","uid":130626,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"3c3c68c3af46385a2775db2626ab1c6b3d88cb13","tid":876903,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T03:12:45.000Z","msg":"首次月經來潮，已夠令女孩子不知所措了，美國一名女孩子更在巴士上遇上這尷尬一幕，但這一切有幸被一個窩心男孩首先發現－－他不動聲色的悄悄告知她情況，還替她解窘，更安慰她說：「我有姊妹，沒問題的別擔心。」<br />\n「我女兒今天在乘巴士回家期間開始來經&hellip;一名較她年長一年的男生&hellip;&hellip;她不太認識的&hellip;&hellip;拉她到一旁，在其耳邊輕聲說她褲子背後有血跡。」一名媽媽在社交網撰文娓娓道來女兒的奇遇，那位男孩子還脫下自己的衞衣，讓她綁在腰間遮掩，以便下巴士走路回家。<br />\n<br />\n「她說她當時很尷尬，只能說那可以了&hellip;&hellip;但那男孩堅持幫忙，還跟她說，『我有姊妹，沒問題的別擔心！（it&rsquo;s all good!）』」女孩的媽媽說罷，特別感謝那男孩的媽媽教養出如此細心的孩子，又解釋自己何以為此事在社交網發帖：「我們聽過很多談及新一代年輕人的壞話，所以我很想分享一些正面的事。」<br />\n此帖一石激起千層浪，感動萬千網民，有人更形容他是一位英雄，難得他不單沒有乘機嘲笑揶揄，還拿出衞衣相助，「那男孩真的很好，竟如此成熟又有同情心拿自己的衞衣給那女孩」。有網民更大讚這是其今年看過最好的分享，或希望自己的兒子也能這樣。<br />\n雖然男孩身份不明，但其貼心舉動令不少網民為之傾心，有人說：「這男孩長大後有天會成為某位幸運女孩的好丈夫。」也有人回應：「我有一種感覺，你女兒應找到一位一輩子的朋友了。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181026/large/1540515417_d6ad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181026%2Flarge%2F1540515417_d6ad.jpg&h=8a99a68a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181025/large/1540448563_24cf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181025%2Flarge%2F1540448563_24cf.jpg&h=382c68b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181026/58833713\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181026%2F58833713&d=XqyKGnwltAFEwUjO9KPbjjCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=41dcf520\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181026%2F58833713&h=dd36e876\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181026/58833713</a>"},{"pid":"4621c3252be8768430886720c8eb6eafc8dbd979","tid":876903,"uid":38041,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T03:14:56.000Z","msg":"真有心 但都唔夠香港男人細心 佢地人仲會準備埋乾淨屎忽同訴訟費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d6b7d262fc3e10917481dd4af9b9e48d1b49fc1","tid":876903,"uid":52939,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"4621c3252be8768430886720c8eb6eafc8dbd979","tid":876903,"uid":38041,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T03:14:56.000Z","msg":"真有心 但都唔夠香港男人細心 佢地人仲會準備埋乾淨屎忽同訴訟費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T03:17:46.000Z","msg":"如果香港或大陸咁做<br />\n可能被人往夠裏打再告性騷擾 不誠實使用紙巾 等等"},{"pid":"420d18b9990972ba02b190868d4f36217ae9788a","tid":876903,"uid":26752,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T03:18:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">嘩<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你流血啊！</span>"},{"pid":"014cd00715ae56e1865ab10d6fe1d476adb8295f","tid":876903,"uid":48161,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T03:19:12.000Z","msg":"咦 你受咗傷呀？"},{"pid":"abb3c0847dc241a27410a454065e7559554f7a63","tid":876903,"uid":3936,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T03:19:48.000Z","msg":"咦 你受左傷啊?"},{"pid":"089125bf5319b974d778147b71cc79c16fc53975","tid":876903,"uid":158585,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"014cd00715ae56e1865ab10d6fe1d476adb8295f","tid":876903,"uid":48161,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T03:19:12.000Z","msg":"咦 你受咗傷呀？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T03:22:15.000Z","msg":"睇到呢句 即刻聽到曹總把聲"},{"pid":"562ef938a81353cec4c2fca796110eb30990f679","tid":876903,"uid":106336,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"0